[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    196[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Priority conflict:** Architecture (A1, model monitoring) vs. Security (S1, IAM least-privilege). Both are HIGH. A1 is more impactful for production viability (a model without monitoring silently degrades). S1 is more impactful for security posture (overly broad permissions are an audit finding). Both should be fixed, but A1 is the more likely production failure mode for a builder following this recipe.
